title: Five Card Stud (1968) Dean Martin · Robert Mitchum

sources.title: Five Card Stud (1968) Dean Martin · Robert Mitchum
sources.description: Colorado 1880: After a poker cheat is lynched by the participants in a poker game, one by one they are killed by a mysterious stranger. Eventually, the avenger also meets his end.   A thrilling and meticulously staged Western. .
